comment on column RRP_MDL.O_ICL_CMM_UNITE_WL_REPAY_DTL.ovdue_repay_flg
  is '逾期还款标志';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_ICL_CMM_UNITE_WL_REPAY_DTL.acru_non_acru_cd
