comment on column RRP_MDL.O_ICL_CMM_UNITE_WL_REPAY_DTL.currt_repay_amt
  is '当期还款金额';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_ICL_CMM_UNITE_WL_REPAY_DTL.currt_repay_pric
  is '当期还款本金';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_ICL_CMM_UNITE_WL_REPAY_DTL.currt_repay_nomal_pric
